********************************************************************************
* 	CHAPTER 3: Control Flow
********************************************************************************

EXPRESSIONS (i=0,printf(),b++) become STATEMENTS when followed by ";" semicolon

Semicolon ";"
	Statment terminator

Braces "{  }"
	Group declarations and statements.
	Compound Statement, Block. 
	Equivalent to a single statement.

--IF---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note: "else" is assigned to closest "if"
if (expression)
	statement1
else
	statement2
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------


---ELSE-IF---------------------------------------------------------------------
if (expression)
	statement
else if (expression)
	statement
else 
	statement
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---SWITCH----------------------------------------------------------------------
switch (expression) {
	case const-expr: statements
	case const-expr: statements
	default: statements
}
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---  DO  ----------------------------------------------------------------------
do
	statement
while (expression);
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
